  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I can go on and tell you that when I was born, we lived on a little street that was nothing but a dirt street with a few houses on it, at the end of which there was a windmill, on a hill.",
      "word_count": 47
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I remember having so much fun climbing on that hill and playing near the windmill and playing everywhere.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In back of us-- we lived in a very small house.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We had a garden.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And at the end of the garden was an outhouse.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There was no running water, so there were-- was no inside plumbing.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And so we had to grow our own vegetables.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And at the end of the garden was an outhouse.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And in back of that was a large orchard.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I remember my brother Maishe, who was four years older than I, and I, as a youngster, stealing fruit from that neighbor's orchard, because we said, well, the threes are leaning over our fence, so we are justified in doing so.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Oh, it was so much fun.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It was really a wonderful childhood.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, look at it this way.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My father was one of eight children.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] In my family, there were eight.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "In all of my father's siblings, there were 7, 8, 9, 10 children.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Therefore, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] just uncles and aunts, I probably had close to 100.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And many of them-- most of them lived in or near Jasionovka.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Now, if you go down one generation, to first cousins, you are talking about probably 200 first cousins.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "To this day, even after the Holocaust, some 15 years ago when we visited Israel, one of my second cousins brought together something like 30 either first, second, or third cousins to meet us.",
      "word_count": 34
    }
  ],
